On the link that they gave there are a series of Q&A's;
Can I get message center posts emailed instead? 
Yes! You can select to have a weekly digest emailed to you and up to two other email addresses. The emailed weekly digest is turned on by default. If you aren't getting your weekly digests, check your spam folder. See the Preferences section of this article for more information on how to set up the weekly digest.
